00:00:07.154 --> 00:00:09.461
[NARRATOR] Previously,
on Dragon Ball Z Kai,

00:00:09.563 --> 00:00:12.437
Majin Buu set off
on a spree of destruction,

00:00:12.539 --> 00:00:15.245
indiscriminately laying waste
to countless cities

00:00:15.346 --> 00:00:17.787
and villages
all across the globe.

00:00:17.887 --> 00:00:20.260
Meanwhile,
sensing Gohan's energy,

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:23.605
Goku transported himself
to the World of the Kais

00:00:23.705 --> 00:00:25.342
and reunited with his son.

00:00:25.442 --> 00:00:28.687
After just one day of training,
Gohan managed to master

00:00:28.787 --> 00:00:32.230
the legendary and
difficult-to-wield Z-Sword.

00:00:32.330 --> 00:00:34.168
To gauge the sword's strength,

00:00:34.268 --> 00:00:38.549
Goku and Gohan put it
to a series of tests.

00:00:38.650 --> 00:00:39.987
[GOKU]
Hike!

00:00:40.087 --> 00:00:42.092
[yells]

00:00:44.601 --> 00:00:46.105
