from the shattered sword.

00:01:01.216 --> 00:01:04.192
Hey, guys. When did
that old man get here?

00:01:04.292 --> 00:01:06.967
[SUPREME KAI]
Excuse me, sir. Who are you?

00:01:07.067 --> 00:01:08.271
Ah, right.

00:01:08.371 --> 00:01:10.846
You'll be very surprised
to learn that I am--

00:01:10.946 --> 00:01:13.220
Oh, I can't wait
to tell you. I...

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:16.697
Oh boy. I'm sorta you.

00:01:16.797 --> 00:01:19.538
