00:14:37.061 --> 00:14:39.703
A-ha! I get it now!

00:14:39.804 --> 00:14:42.946
[laughs]
Goku, you crazy rascal, you!

00:14:43.046 --> 00:14:45.822
Who better to
beat a blob like Buu?

00:14:45.922 --> 00:14:48.830
What do you think
he's about to do?

00:14:50.770 --> 00:14:53.343
[yells, grunts]

00:14:53.444 --> 00:14:55.518
[YAMCHA]
I think he's starting to run.

00:15:04.678 --> 00:15:06.450
[panting]

00:15:06.551 --> 00:15:08.691
[ALL]
Aah!

00:15:08.791 --> 00:15:12.603
[ROSHI] A-ha. Well,
this was a total bust.

00:15:12.703 --> 00:15:13.739
[PICCOLO]
I figured.

00:15:13.839 --> 00:15:16.815
--Kids, pay attention.
--Huh?!

00:15:16.915 --> 00:15:19.021
This happened 'cause
when you said "--sion,"

00:15:19.121 --> 00:15:20.727
Trunks had
his fingers sticking out.

00:15:20.827 --> 00:15:24.572
But at that part, both of you
are supposed to be making fists.

00:15:24.672 --> 00:15:27.514
Hm. See?

00:15:27.614 --> 00:15:29.654
Okay? Got it?

00:15:30.421 --> 00:15:33.363
[PICCOLO] All right.
Let's try this again.

00:15:35.203 --> 00:15:37.644
Well? Go on and change back!

00:15:37.744 --> 00:15:40.485
[grunts]
So how do I do that?

00:15:40.586 --> 00:15:42.525
Ah!

00:15:44.062 --> 00:15:47.540
[grunts]
We've got no choice.

00:15:47.640 --> 00:15:50.180
We'll just have to wait
for 30 minutes to pass.

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:53.526
[KRILLIN] This is crazy!
You're not Trunks or Goten!

00:15:53.626 --> 00:15:54.862
What gives?

00:15:54.962 --> 00:15:57.269
[ROSHI] How'd you get
that strange new outfit?

00:15:57.369 --> 00:16:00.244
[VIDEL] So, what happened
to Goten and Trunks?

00:16:00.344 --> 00:16:02.886
[GOTENKS]
Uh. Ah. Uhh...

00:16:02.987 --> 00:16:04.423
[YAMCHA]
Do you have a name, big guy?

00:16:04.525 --> 00:16:05.962
Yeah, Gotenks.

00:16:06.062 --> 00:16:10.407
Aah! You see?
So it is Gotenks after all!

00:16:12.816 --> 00:16:14.152
[MR. POPO]
Thirty minutes has passed.

00:16:14.252 --> 00:16:16.392
Should be any moment now.

00:16:20.673 --> 00:16:22.579
[ROSHI yelps]

00:16:23.013 --> 00:16:24.249
[GOTEN, TRUNKS]
Uaah!

00:16:24.349 --> 00:16:26.489
--[BULMA] Oh, it's Trunks!
--[CHICHI] Goten!

00:16:28.530 --> 00:16:29.800
So, did we fuse?

00:16:29.900 --> 00:16:31.137
I don't know.

00:16:31.237 --> 00:16:32.909
Oh, come on guys;
what'd it feel like?

00:16:33.009 --> 00:16:34.648
When you two merged?

00:16:34.748 --> 00:16:37.355
So you can't remember,
is that what you're saying?

00:16:37.455 --> 00:16:38.627
Uh-huh.

00:16:38.727 --> 00:16:41.367
Well, you should be proud;
you really pulled it off!

00:16:41.467 --> 00:16:44.579
And you have given us
a ray of hope!

00:16:44.679 --> 00:16:46.282
[footsteps]

00:16:46.382 --> 00:16:48.724
Could everyone please
save their conversations

00:16:48.824 --> 00:16:50.294
until after the battle is over?

00:16:50.394 --> 00:16:53.103
Right now,
every little second counts.

00:16:53.203 --> 00:16:56.312
Boys, let's try again!

00:17:02.029 --> 00:17:04.036
And begin!

00:17:04.136 --> 00:17:08.750
[BOTH]
Fu...sion! Ha!

00:17:08.850 --> 00:17:11.156
[PICCOLO grunts]

00:17:20.553 --> 00:17:25.868
[GOTENKS groans]

00:17:25.969 --> 00:17:27.941
Strike two.
They botched it again.

00:17:28.041 --> 00:17:29.545
Sure looks that way.

00:17:29.646 --> 00:17:31.719
He hasn't even
done anything yet

00:17:31.819 --> 00:17:33.558
and already he looks exhausted.

00:17:33.658 --> 00:17:35.530
[PICCOLO] Ugh! This time,
at "Ha!" your fingers

00:17:35.632 --> 00:17:37.937
weren't lined up
correctly. Go again!

00:17:38.037 --> 00:17:41.180
[inhales]

00:17:41.280 --> 00:17:45.459
[coughing]

00:17:45.560 --> 00:17:48.535
Well, in 30 minutes, of course.

00:17:52.749 --> 00:17:54.554
Okay. It's time!

00:17:54.655 --> 00:17:56.660
[grunts]

00:18:00.773 --> 00:18:06.791
[BOTH]
Fu...sion. Ha!

00:18:11.370 --> 00:18:13.510
[PICCOLO]
That was perfect!

00:18:14.915 --> 00:18:17.289
We're witnessing the birth

00:18:17.389 --> 00:18:21.534
of the warrior who will
defeat Majin Buu!

00:18:28.824 --> 00:18:31.899
[ALL groan]

00:18:31.999 --> 00:18:33.938
Holy cow!

00:18:37.182 --> 00:18:38.218
[gasps]

00:18:38.318 --> 00:18:40.290
Whoa! That was
some energy blast!

00:18:40.391 --> 00:18:42.296
And it worked!
It actually worked!

00:18:42.396 --> 00:18:44.002
I can't believe it!

00:18:44.102 --> 00:18:45.205
Incredible!

00:18:45.305 --> 00:18:46.645
I'm no expert,
but it does seem like

00:18:46.745 --> 00:18:48.817
the boys did a pretty good
job this time.

00:18:48.917 --> 00:18:51.390
Well, judging by his appearance,
he does look stronger.

00:18:51.490 --> 00:18:53.163
Yeah, he does! Even I can tell

00:18:53.263 --> 00:18:55.302
he's rocking some
out-of-this-world power!

00:18:55.402 --> 00:18:58.278
I mean, just look
at him; he's amazing!

00:18:58.378 --> 00:19:00.484
[PICCOLO]
Ha! You finally got it right.

00:19:00.585 --> 00:19:02.256
Now we just have
to wait 30 minutes

00:19:02.356 --> 00:19:04.932
so you can do it again,
this time at Super Saiyan.

00:19:05.032 --> 00:19:06.202
Uh, uh, uh!

00:19:06.302 --> 00:19:08.341
You're underestimating
my awesomeness!

00:19:08.441 --> 00:19:09.779
'Scuse me?

00:19:09.879 --> 00:19:11.417
I'm more than strong enough
now to wipe the floor

00:19:11.518 --> 00:19:12.922
with that Buu guy!

00:19:13.022 --> 00:19:14.359
You fool! What are you saying?

00:19:14.459 --> 00:19:16.399
You don't know the first
thing about Majin Buu.

00:19:16.499 --> 00:19:17.937
Or how fierce he can be!

00:19:18.037 --> 00:19:19.677
I don't care how much
stronger you've grown,

00:19:19.777 --> 00:19:21.581
you're still no match
for that beast!

00:19:21.682 --> 00:19:25.594
Trust me. You're simply
not ready to face him yet!

00:19:25.695 --> 00:19:29.673
Hah! So, you doubt me?

00:19:29.773 --> 00:19:32.547
Fine. Doubt me.
I'll just have to show you.

00:19:32.648 --> 00:19:34.922
Show you Buu's
dead body, that is!

00:19:35.022 --> 00:19:36.559
Uuuh--

00:19:37.495 --> 00:19:41.139
--[ALL gasp]
--Hey! Trunten! Gotrunks!

00:19:42.410 --> 00:19:44.551
[MR. POPO]
Almost Piccolo; it's Gotenks.

00:19:44.651 --> 00:19:46.556
Aha! Buu's over there.

00:19:46.656 --> 00:19:48.227
And close enough
for me to whoop his butt

00:19:48.327 --> 00:19:50.000
and still make it
back to the Lookout

00:19:50.100 --> 00:19:52.674
with plenty of time to spare!

00:19:57.589 --> 00:19:59.026
Wow! He's so fast!

00:19:59.127 --> 00:20:01.568
[PICCOLO] That arrogant punk!
If he gets himself killed,

00:20:01.668 --> 00:20:03.842
all our hopes for survival
will die with him!

00:20:03.942 --> 00:20:05.982
Well, this combo kid
may be a little bit cocky,

00:20:06.082 --> 00:20:07.720
but Goku was sure
he'd be strong enough,

00:20:07.820 --> 00:20:09.793
so maybe this isn't
a total disaster.

00:20:09.893 --> 00:20:11.597
That's right.
Seemed pretty certain.

00:20:11.698 --> 00:20:14.606
Maybe he knows
something we don't.

00:20:19.387 --> 00:20:25.774
[GOKU snoring]

00:20:28.415 --> 00:20:30.721
Ah-choo!

00:20:35.971 --> 00:20:39.347
[yawns]

00:20:39.447 --> 00:20:42.290
You have a nice
nap there, Goku?

00:20:42.390 --> 00:20:46.670
Hey, Supreme Kai, how goes it?

00:20:46.771 --> 00:20:49.378
Hm? Where's Gohan at?
Is he all powered-up

00:20:49.478 --> 00:20:52.453
and finished with
that silly ceremony yet?

00:20:52.554 --> 00:20:59.943
[ELDER KAI hollers]

00:21:00.043 --> 00:21:01.614
Never ends!

00:21:01.714 --> 00:21:03.888
You weren't out long.
It's only been two hours.

00:21:03.989 --> 00:21:05.292
So, we've got at
least another three

00:21:05.392 --> 00:21:08.434
before he finishes the
ceremony. Best settle in.

00:21:08.535 --> 00:21:10.810
Hey! Gohan! How's your power?

00:21:10.910 --> 00:21:15.022
Jeez, Dad. Really?
You're so not helping.

00:21:15.122 --> 00:21:22.109
[ELDER KAI continues]

00:21:22.209 --> 00:21:24.584
[NARRATOR]
The boys' Fusion was a success.

00:21:24.684 --> 00:21:27.794
However, only time
will tell if Gohan can also

00:21:27.894 --> 00:21:32.307
power up using the supernatural
gift of the Supreme Kai

00:21:32.407 --> 00:21:34.881
from 15 generations ago.

00:21:34.981 --> 00:21:38.158
The moment of Earth's
annihilation draws closer,

00:21:38.258 --> 00:21:40.764
next Dragon Ball Z Kai!

00:21:41.702 --> 00:21:46.884
♪ Closing Song ♪

00:22:46.997 --> 00:22:48.334
[GOKU]
Hey! It's me, Goku!

00:22:48.434 --> 00:22:50.943
The good news is, you've got
Fusion down perfectly.

00:22:51.043 --> 00:22:53.985
The bad news is, it may have
changed your personalities, too.

00:22:54.085 --> 00:22:55.289
[GOTENKS]
Ha-ha-ha!

00:22:55.389 --> 00:22:58.030
Going toe-to-toe against
the great Gotenks,

00:22:58.130 --> 00:23:00.705
Majin Buu doesn't
stand a chance!

00:23:00.805 --> 00:23:03.178
[GOKU] Next time
on Dragon Ball Z Kai:

00:23:07.157 --> 00:23:10.199
[GOHAN] You really think
he can defeat Majin Buu?

